        <num>CC 944</num>
        <heading>944.  Prescription</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 944.  Prescription
An action to declare a successor unworthy is subject to a liberative prescription of five years from the death of the decedent as to intestate successors and five years from the probate of the will as to testate successors.</p>
        </content>
